# Excel Dashboard Template
# This file represents the structure for creating a comprehensive DAC analysis dashboard

# Worksheet 1: Main Data
# - Contains the complete pipeline output
# - All project data with DAC analysis
# - Source for all other worksheets

# Worksheet 2: Executive Summary
# - High-level metrics and KPIs
# - Charts showing DAC vs non-DAC distribution
# - Investment priority breakdown

# Worksheet 3: Geographic Analysis
# - Projects by county and region
# - DAC concentration mapping
# - Rural vs urban distribution

# Worksheet 4: Data Quality Report
# - Geocoding success rates
# - Missing data analysis
# - Recommendations for data improvement

# Worksheet 5: Investment Recommendations
# - Projects sorted by priority tier
# - Budget allocation suggestions
# - Community impact projections